				</p>
				<div class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
					<strong>Typical outcome:</strong> Portfolio companies ship faster, better technical execution
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Testimonials placeholder -->
		<div class="mt-20 text-center">
			<div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12">
